.SH NAME
gnb-config-convert - Convert config to another format


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgnb config convert [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Convert the active config file to a different format (TOML, YAML, or JSON).
Example:
  gnb config convert --to yaml
  gnb config convert --to json


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for convert

.PP
\fB--to\fP=""
	Target format (toml, yaml, json)


